{"tid":1229310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［好打得］路透社：北京嚴重懷疑林鄭能力","createTime":"2019-06-16T01:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:01:16.000Z","uid":4206,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d4847e2c61347ecd8c2f5696783045d685ee1b66","tid":1229310,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥昨日（15日）宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，路透社今日（16日）引述「一個在北京跟中央領導有聯繫，並會定期跟高官見面的消息來源」（a source in Beijing with ties to China&rsquo;s leadership who meets regularly with senior officials）稱，北京在特區政府處理今次風波拙劣後，「如今對林鄭月娥的能力有嚴重懷疑」（Beijing now had severe doubts about Lam&rsquo;s capabilities）。報道引述國務院及中聯辦均拒即時回應有關消息。<br />\n<br />\n報道另引述一些早前曾跟林鄭月娥會面的商界和外國領事館人員稱，林鄭月娥對北京在面對中美貿易戰和南海緊張局勢升溫下，她仍強推《逃犯條例》修訂，表現得「無動於中以妥協」（appeared in no mood to compromise）。報道引述有政治評論員稱，林鄭月娥的管治已陷倒數。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190616/s00001/1560644824819/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%b7%af%e9%80%8f%e7%a4%be-%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e5%9a%b4%e9%87%8d%e6%87%b7%e7%96%91%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e8%83%bd%e5%8a%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190616%2Fs00001%2F1560644824819%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%2580%258f%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e5%258c%2597%25e4%25ba%25ac%25e5%259a%25b4%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%2587%25b7%25e7%2596%2591%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e8%2583%25bd%25e5%258a%259b&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=8f9f646b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190616%2Fs00001%2F1560644824819%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%2580%258f%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e5%258c%2597%25e4%25ba%25ac%25e5%259a%25b4%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%258